    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Preliminary discussions are now taking place with India, to be followed by similar discussions with Egypt and Iraq.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-287c5b63-eb35-459e-8816-e54073bc80f4" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
